{
  "stem": "20800.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I start-- I knew that they don't really want to talk because I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They stop talking, so that's what I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And somebody went to told-- and told Secret Service.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What did they say?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they said that I said-- in Russia I will tell you, they will now-- yes, [SPEAKING RUSSIAN] But you see, I could say it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's like there is Jews and the bloody Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because of bloody Jews, Jews are bad, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like in every one nationality.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's nothing to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you see, this time, you should-- you shouldn't say [? shit ?] because that was a very bad say.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said before, Stalin said-- Stalin could put in prison for the word [? shit, ?] but there was difference between me saying shit and Russian or Ukraine or others saying [? shit. ?] I could say [? shit ?] because I am [? shit, ?] and I can criticize that there is bad Jews and good Jews.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because of bad Jews, good Jews suffer, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the person went and told what I said, and that was enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In two days, they called me in the Secret Service, special Secret Service, and told me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember it was-- it was in January, not February, because it was very cold, very bad-- it was winter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't found then yet not my parents, not my sister, nobody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was looking all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As soon they just free me, I was looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't find nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this, this was Captain Smirnov, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He called me and said that we have special transport for people to Russia, and you can go to Russia now.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will provide with special wagon and things like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
